    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S65 4.0L V8. The engine features individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system, delivering linear power delivery up to a staggering 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis retains its structural rigidity, supported by M-specific subframe bracing and lightweight aluminum suspension components that significantly reduce unsprung mass for precise turn-in. Power is managed through a traditional 6-speed manual transmission with a crisp gate feel, linked to a factory M Variable Differential Lock that ensures optimal torque distribution during high-lateral-G cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive throttle actuator service and a cooling system pressure test to ensure peak thermal efficiency. This vehicle exhibits sharp mechanical feedback and robust longitudinal dynamics, catering to the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency.",
